tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE TherapeuticInterventions (
  intervention_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  intervention_name VARCHAR(255),
  intervention_type VARCHAR(50),
  outcome_measurements JSONB,
  effectiveness_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  diagnosis TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Interventions (
  intervention_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  intervention_name VARCHAR(255),
  target_population TEXT,
  efficacy_rating INT,
  cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
);
CREATE TABLE interventions ( id INT PRIMARY KEY, intervention_name VARCHAR(255), intervention_type VARCHAR(255), effectiveness_score FLOAT );

CREATE TABLE patients ( patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY, patient_name VARCHAR(255), date_of_birth DATE, gender VARCHAR(10), intervention_id INT, FOREIGN KEY (intervention_id) REFERENCES interventions(id) );
CREATE TABLE outcomes ( outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY, patient_id INT, FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patients(patient_id), measurement_date DATE, outcome_measure FLOAT, outcome_type VARCHAR(50) );

CREATE TABLE PatientData (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    patient_age INT,
    patient_gender VARCHAR(10),
    intervention_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (intervention_id) REFERENCES TherapeuticInterventions(intervention_id)
);

CREATE TABLE OutcomeMeasurements (
    measurement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    measurement_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    measurement_value FLOAT,
    patient_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES PatientData(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE DataAnalysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    analysis_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    analysis_details TEXT,
    measurement_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (measurement_id) REFERENCES OutcomeMeasurements(measurement_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Intervention (intervention_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
intervention_name STRING,
intervention_description STRING,
intervention_type STRING,
intervention_duration INT,
intervention_cost DECIMAL);

CREATE TABLE Patient (patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
patient_name STRING,
patient_age INT,
patient_gender STRING,
patient_diagnosis STRING,
admission_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE Evaluation (evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
evaluation_date DATE,
patient_id INT,
intervention_id INT,
outcome_score INT,
feedback TEXT);

CREATE TABLE OutcomeMeasurement (measurement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
evaluation_id INT,
measurement_date DATE,
measurement_type STRING,
measurement_result FLOAT,
measurement_unit STRING);

CREATE TABLE Therapist (therapist_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
therapist_name STRING,
therapist_specialization STRING,
therapist_experience_years INT,
therapist_contact_info STRING,
therapist_location STRING);
